# Alerts
for alerts always use client/src/components/common/CustomAlert.js
# Data
for data have to call backend, if needed, create the service for abstracting the api logic from the view
# Styles
always create custom stylesheets, dont use tailwind
# Games
use GameAccessPanel for showing the available games, use GameAlert for notifying correct or incorrect answers, use GameSummary for the final view after the gameview.
# ListView
for creating lists or tables, use the component client/src/components/common/List.js
# Navigation
add the route on App.js and config/navigation.js and use the hook useNavigation for getting the authorized routes